# Backend stack

- **Framework:** FastAPI with Pydantic v2 schemas.
- **Primary DB:** MongoDB (Pydantic documents, versioned index scripts).
- **Secondary DB:** PostgreSQL for FTS search and audit (Alembic migrations).
- **Style:** Ruff; type hints on all functions; async for I/O-bound work.
- **Functions:** Keep under 88 lines.
- **Migrations:** Alembic when Postgres models change; Mongo index scripts when collections/indexes are added.
- **Logging:** Log important actions; never log secrets or tokens.
